                                                               throws JavaDocParsingException
        Description copied from interface: JavaDocParsing
        Collects data from JavaDocs saved in given folder and returns it's representation.
        Specified by:
        parseDataFromJavaDoc in interface JavaDocParsing
        Parameters:
        javaDocFolder - Folder where are saved JavaDocs. This folder is the folder described with @code{-d} parameter when using @code{javadoc} command in command line.

        JavaDocParsingException
